<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RetroSprint — Synthwave Miro Retro Template</title>
    <meta name="description" content="A vibrant, synthwave-themed Miro retrospective template with structured zones for What Went Well, To Improve, and Action Items. Free to use.">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="glow-bg"></div>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">RetroSprint</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#features">Features</a>
            <a href="#preview">Preview</a>
            <a href="#how-it-works">How It Works</a>
            <a href="#cta" class="btn-nav">Get Template</a>
        </div>
        <button class="mobile-menu-btn" aria-label="Toggle menu">
            <span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </button>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <span class="badge">Free Miro Template</span>
            <h1>Retros That <span class="gradient-text">Actually Feel Like Flow</span></h1>
            <p>Ditch the boring whiteboards. RetroSprint is a synthwave-themed Miro retrospective template with structured zones for reflection, improvement, and action — designed to make sprint retros engaging.</p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <a href="#cta" class="btn-primary">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
                    Get the Template
                </a>
                <a href="#preview" class="btn-outline">See Preview</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-image">
            <div class="glass-card">
                <img src="preview.png" alt="RetroSprint Miro Template — three neon columns for What Went Well, To Improve, and Action Items">
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="features" class="features">
        <div class="section-header">
            <span class="badge">Why RetroSprint</span>
            <h2>Built for Teams That Care About Retros</h2>
            <p>Three structured zones, one cohesive aesthetic, zero setup friction.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-wrap"><svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--secondary)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg></div>
                <h3>One-Click Import</h3>
                <p>Copy the template directly into your Miro workspace. No plugins, no config — just open and go.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-wrap"><svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Three Clear Zones</h3>
                <p>Pre-built columns for <strong>What Went Well</strong>, <strong>To Improve</strong>, and <strong>Action Items</strong> keep discussions focused.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-wrap"><svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent-bright)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 14s1.5 2 4 2 4-2 4-2"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9.01" y2="9"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15.01" y2="9"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Aesthetic That Energizes</h3>
                <p>Synthwave neon palette with custom sticky note styles that make retros feel less like a chore, more like a vibe.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-wrap"><svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--secondary)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Voting Ready</h3>
                <p>Built-in voting areas so your team can prioritize what matters without extra tooling.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-wrap"><svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Team-Friendly</h3>
                <p>Works for remote, hybrid, and co-located teams. Everyone sees the same beautiful board in real time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-wrap"><svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent-bright)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/><line x1="9" y1="21" x2="9" y2="9"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Fully Customizable</h3>
                <p>Move, resize, recolor anything. It's your Miro board — the template is just a starting point.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="preview" class="preview">
        <div class="preview-inner">
            <div class="preview-text">
                <span class="badge">Template Preview</span>
                <h2>See What Your Retro Will Look Like</h2>
                <p>Three neon-lit columns on a dark grid. Sticky notes that pop. A layout that guides the conversation from celebration to action.</p>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--secondary)" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                        Custom neon sticky notes per zone
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--secondary)" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                        Built-in dot voting stations
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--secondary)" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                        Action item tracker with owners
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--secondary)" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                        Icebreaker zone to warm up the team
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="preview-image">
                <div class="preview-frame">
                    <div class="frame-dots">
                        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
                    </div>
                    <img src="preview.png" alt="RetroSprint template detail showing three columns with neon sticky notes">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="how-it-works" class="how-it-works">
        <div class="section-header">
            <span class="badge">3 Steps</span>
            <h2>Up and Running in Under a Minute</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <h3>Grab the Template</h3>
                <p>Click the link below to open the template in Miro.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-connector"><svg width="40" height="20" viewBox="0 0 40 20"><path d="M0 10 L30 10 L25 5 M30 10 L25 15" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" fill="none" opacity="0.5"/></svg></div>
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <h3>Duplicate to Your Board</h3>
                <p>Use Miro's "Use template" button to copy it into your workspace.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-connector"><svg width="40" height="20" viewBox="0 0 40 20"><path d="M0 10 L30 10 L25 5 M30 10 L25 15" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" fill="none" opacity="0.5"/></svg></div>
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <h3>Run Your Retro</h3>
                <p>Invite your team and start adding sticky notes. It's that simple.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="cta" class="cta-section">
        <div class="cta-card">
            <h2>Ready to Upgrade Your Retros?</h2>
            <p>Free forever. No sign-up required. Just open, duplicate, and run.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn-primary btn-large">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg>
                Open in Miro
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <div class="footer-logo">RetroSprint</div>
            <p>A free Miro retrospective template. Made with neon and good vibes.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
